        <div class="item">
            <span>
                About JNHRC
            </span>
            <div class="description">
                <p>
                    Journal of Nepal Health Research Council (JNHRC) an official, internationally peer reviewed, Pubmed
                    Indxed, biomedical journal of the Nepal Health Research Council (NHRC) since 2002. It is published
                    three monthly and publishes articles on the following category: Original Article, Review Article,
                    Case Report, Viewpoint and Letter to the Editor and others. The aim of JNHRC is to increase the
                    visibility and ease of use of open access scientific and scholarly articles thereby promoting their
                    increased usage and impact. Hence, JNHRC grants the permission to read, download, copy, distribute,
                    print, search, or link to the full texts of these articles which is available online (http://
                    jnhrc.com.np) freely. Authors do not have to pay for submission, processing or publication of
                    articles at JNHRC.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
